{"tid":1842323,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"利用世界各地武漢肺炎確診數字 逆向推算武漢受感染人數","createTime":"2020-01-25T15:31:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-26T15:35:03.000Z","uid":280744,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"2cbe9b4fbf6cfef9e41527c506b95ea0ec33dcdb","tid":1842323,"uid":280744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T15:31:10.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://australia51.com/article/6D362133-EF0E-191F-BAAE-5B4B19885D7F/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faustralia51.com%2Farticle%2F6D362133-EF0E-191F-BAAE-5B4B19885D7F%2F&d=DF3UGDbnXTwcWfCLvBafJVYPZSwMlx1ag7qd%2FaAfmLs%3D&h=526a91ac\" target=\"_blank\">https://australia51.com/article/6D362133-EF0E-191F-BAAE-5B4B19885D7F/</a><br />\n<br />\n利用外國確診數字推算中國武漢感染人數<br />\n<br />\n根據上述資料12月30號到1月20號<br />\n經武漢機場飛往世界各地的航班資料座位表顯示 <br />\n有113502機位飛到外國<br />\n全球確診個案最新顯示為36宗<br />\n得出外國確診染病機率為0.000317175<br />\n<br />\n武漢市大約900萬人，周邊城市超過2000萬人 會選擇武漢機場。<br />\n<br />\n如果以2000萬人x確診機率，計算結果為1月20日前 武漢和周邊城市6343人受到感染。<br />\n<br />\n備注：<br />\n1:以上計算資料基於只有航班客位數字，每一個航班都不可能100%坐滿，所以實際感染人數會比上述數字更加多<br />\n2:因為航班資料截至1月20號，外國的武漢人很有可能還在潛伏期，沒有病發確診數字很大機會會再度上升，所以實際感染人數會比上述數字更加多"},{"pid":"75b8995fd605e5b90796399c94b3cf6444139cd2","tid":1842323,"uid":28068,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T20:09:57.000Z","msg":"完全唔準<br />\n6343<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9386d64d30d632095d1d3cf6d6b30705feff9d86","tid":1842323,"uid":101554,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T21:43:26.000Z","msg":"有道理 數量級應該係啱嘅 ( 千位數 )<br />\n睇返官方數據其實都差唔多<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0b08c007e147ae6341296bb29a1f4bf61ada3b7","tid":1842323,"uid":156121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T22:00:48.000Z","msg":"人地估緊270000-340000"},{"pid":"4339c3edc37d86bb31d74a2a1d530c6577cf7f0f","tid":1842323,"uid":156121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b0b08c007e147ae6341296bb29a1f4bf61ada3b7","tid":1842323,"uid":156121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T22:00:48.000Z","msg":"人地估緊270000-340000"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T22:01:38.000Z","msg":"btw 呢個數係咩都唔做到2月4號既數字(好似係<br />\n詳情要睇番imperial份paper"},{"pid":"68a476732455ffb030775059dec3524eee9634ed","tid":1842323,"uid":288609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T15:35:03.000Z","msg":"(未fc) 騰訊誤報未經維穩嘅確診數字<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1844229\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1844229</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n識睇一定係睇官方，漏出嚟嘅資訊。"}]}